      <byline class="print_byline">By PATRICIA WINTERS LAURO</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Lauro, Patricia Winters</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Tim McHale is named to new post of chief media director at DDB Digital, part of DDB Worldwide (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Tim McHale was named to the new post of chief media officer, responsible for North America, at DDB Digital, New York, part of the DDB Worldwide unit of the Omnicom Group. He had been executive vice president and director for strategic planning and development at i-traffic, New York, part of Agency.com.</p>
      </block>
